com.microsoft.azure.management.resources.fluentcore.arm.collection

Interface SupportsGettingByName<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the resource collection
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Deployments, Features.InResourceProvider, Providers, ResourceGroups, Subscriptions

    public interface SupportsGettingByName<T>
    Provides access to getting a specific Azure resource based on its name within the current resource group.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      T getByName(String name)
      Gets the information about a resource from Azure based on the resource name within the current resource group.

     throws CloudException,
            IOException
        Gets the information about a resource from Azure based on the resource name within the current resource group.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the resource. (Note, this is not the resource ID.)

        an immutable representation of the resource
        Throws:
        CloudException - exceptions thrown from the cloud
        IOException - exceptions thrown from serialization/deserialization
